response.original_title: Under the Trees of Hampstead Heath, I Ate Fei Larm Char Rice
response.overview: On a quiet afternoon beneath the trees of Hampstead Heath, Fan eats Fei Larm Char Rice (肥腩叉飯), and ponders deeply on what’s missing from the taste of her rice.
response.title: Under the Trees of Hampstead Heath, I Ate Fei Larm Char Rice
